reports together show that prices were extremely volatile early in the year.=
=20
"All the prices were high," he said, noting the downward trend in costs sinc=
e=20
his agency began buying power in mid-January.=20
The average price per megawatt-hour for all state purchases went from $316 i=
n=20
January to $243 in May. Spot prices fell from an average of $321 per hour to=
=20
$271, the reports show.=20
