Enron was based on politics, not facts." Spokesmen for BC Hydro could not be=
=20
reached late Monday to comment on its huge sales to the state. In the past,=20
the utility has defended its pricing practices, saying it has offered=20
last-minute hydroelectric power that helped keep California's lights on.=20
